  Using Reference Images

In this video, I'll show you how to use reference images to create image-inspired renders inside Midjourney.

  • Link to Car Image
  • Link to Film Still

Image Weight Code: --iw .5

  • Pick a number between 0 and 5, 1 is default.
  • The reference image will be prioritized based on the weight you give it.
